# {SERVER_NAME}

MCP server providing {API_NAME} integration for Claude Code.

## Installation

### Claude Code

```bash
claude mcp add {name} --scope user -- uv run --directory {ABSOLUTE_PATH} {SERVER_NAME}
```

### VS Code

Add to `.vscode/settings.json` or user settings:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "{name}": {
      "command": "uv",
      "args": ["run", "--directory", "{ABSOLUTE_PATH}", "{SERVER_NAME}"]
    }
  }
}
```

## Environment Variables

Create `.env` in the project root or add to `~/.claude/.env`:

```
{API_KEY_VAR}=your_api_key_here
```

